<br>
What I need to know, however, is how to port up there without getting my wizard killed. I know I can get to the book without dying, now that I've had some practice. But now that my entire guild knows never to go to PoH with me again, I need a near-guaranteed way to get up there without a repeat of my accident. (Wizard and Paladin dying, bring two guild groups up to get corpses, everyone dies, have to call for an uber guild to come rescue us)<br>
<br>
Someone brought up the idea of invising the wizard. Can this be done successfully while the wizard is casting, and it will remain on him after he zones in? If so, then we should be able to get him rezzed down in the same fashion, and he shouldn't need more than 3 minutes, so he can probably use the dueling method. <br>
<br>
However, does a dueling death cause oom upon respawning? If so, he will probably use up most of the 3 minutes medding to cast alter plane, and zoning will most likely take the rest of the time.<br>
<br>
Hmm, if this works, perhaps I can count on another PoH run soon.<br>
<br>
Edit: And no, I didn't bring all my gear with me. I used the rez-down trick.. or would have, but the cleric left. Oh well, at least I never had to pay him. Next time, I'll wait until I get a guild cleric. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugeredshadowblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gered Shadowblade</A> at: 3/31/02 3:15:17 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usigpaos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sigpaos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/2/02 1:11:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13809.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoH solo run.. any last advice?</span><hr size=1> Group with the suicidal wizard and another that can cast invis. When you're ready to head up, have yourself invis'd and then have the 3rd person start casting invis on the wizard. Right before invis casts, have the wizard start casting the PoH port. Both of you will be invis'd and as soon as the wizard zones into hate, have the cleric res them.<br>
<br>
The book has an 8 hour respawn time so if its not up, check back in every couple hours.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure if its safe any longer, but the balcony over the Maestro organ had a safe area by the wall, you might be able to camp out there.<br>
